---

This project bundles and redistributes assets from third-party software.

## TuiCss

The compiled CSS, fonts, and image assets distributed with this package are
built from the SCSS sources, fonts, and images of TuiCss, vendored under
`vendor/tuicss/` and rebuilt at publish time.

  TuiCss — https://github.com/vinibiavatti1/TuiCss
  Copyright (c) 2019 Vinicius Reif Biavatti
  Licensed under the MIT License (see `vendor/tuicss/LICENSE`).

## Perfect DOS VGA 437 font

The bundled font "Perfect DOS VGA 437" (distributed in `dist/fonts/`) is
included via TuiCss and is free to use and redistribute. See
`vendor/tuicss/fonts/dos437.txt` and `vendor/tuicss/NOTICE.md` for details.
